Danny is joined by Katie Cazorla to recap this week's Vanderpump Rules. They discuss the new beer cheese venture from Brittany and Jax, Peter's finances, Ken, and lots more. Danny also recap's this week's #RHOA.


Katie Cazorla/#PumpRules Recap: 5:20

#RHOA Recap: 47:45ish
